track_notes: Look at the recommendations F/AM-564 Crete de La Madone

Just because of the covid restriction, i planned this track, witch is 1000m up starting from the Chaudan were is a few parking places for car. There is no path to reach the summit and you must use MODE SANGLIER. No water except on departure.
track_title: The most difficult way to Huesti

track_notes: Nice walk; a bit difficult around the summit. you can park at the village; not so much room! To climb the last part to the summi, there is no path, in the forest, if you go down south do not follow this track absolutely; better to go south-east
